```py
mt-set :: Set
is-in :: (T, Set<T> -> Bool)
insert :: (T, Set<T> -> Set<T>)
union :: (Set<T>, Set<T> -> Set<T>)
size :: (Set<T> -> Number)
to-list :: (Set<T> -> List<T>)
```

```py
fun size<T>(s :: LSet<T>) -> Number:
  s.length()
end
```

```py
fun size<T>(s :: LSet<T>) -> Number:
  cases (List) s:
    | empty => 0
    | link(f, r) =>
      if r.member(f):
        size(r)
      else:
        1 + size(r)
      end
  end
end
```
